"""
ARE Analysis — SKY Breathwork RCT
==================================
Reproduces all AU-rich element enrichment statistics and figures
reported in Singh et al. (2025), Nature Communications submission.

Input files (same directory as this script):
  - 02_ARE_annotations.csv   : per-gene AREScore, 7-mer counts,
                                ITT logFC, group assignments
  - 03_RBP_specificity.csv   : precomputed RBP OR/CI/p/rho
                                (used for figure only; all statistics
                                 recomputed below for verification)

Output:
  - Fig_S1_CDF_7mer.pdf
  - Fig_S2_partial_Spearman.pdf
  - Fig_6C_ARE_bar.pdf
  - Fig_6D_RBP_forest.pdf
  - ARE_statistics_verified.csv

Dependencies:
  pip install pandas numpy scipy matplotlib seaborn

Citation for partial Spearman method:
  Mukherjee N et al. Genome Biol. 2014;15(1):R12.

Citation for AREScore:
  Spasic M et al. PLoS Genet. 2012;8(1):e1002433.

Citation for ARED-Plus database:
  Bakheet T et al. Nucleic Acids Res. 2018;46(D1):D218-D220.
"""

